data.title: Bjorkman Helps Woodbridge to His Seventh Men's Doubles Title
data.meta_description: LONDON - Todd Woodbridge Won His Seventh Men's Doubles Title at Wimbledon Yesterday When He and His Swedish Partner, Jonas Bjorkman, Defeated Daniel Nestor and Mark Knowles 6-1 6-2 6-7 7-5 in the Final.
